name: A Short and Winding Road
description:
A representation of my friend @andekaaa_'s photography work (check him on instagram if you want to see the original). It's always interesting to see his perspective in capturing things, especially old building objects and how great he is at giving 'drama' in the static images he shoots.

As if talking to me!

Actual location:
J. Tanjungpura, Pontianak, West Kalimantan, Indonesia
